NUMBER 1224
NAME Small Cave
CAVE
DARKNESS
REGION 15
CHANNEL 68
MONSTER_GROUP 50
CALL 69
MINEA
CALL 33
*DESCRIPTION_START
The air is decidedly chilly here, and very damp. Moisture condenses on
every smooth surface, dripping to the gray stone floor with tiny pattering
sounds that echo in the stillness. A cool draft brings the sound of gentle
waves from down a low tunnel. Rivulets of water run down the walls and
join into a larger stream running southwest.
*DESCRIPTION_END
EXIT W 1223
EXIT SW 1226
ITEM 0 77 ADJ1=396 ADJ2=267 VAL2=1225
; low rough tunnel (to Underground Lake)
EXTEND 0 carved through the stone by running water
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAMINE 0
The ceiling is lower than is comfortable for the average human, but
considering that nature alone crafted this, it is quite large and sturdy.
*DESCRIPTION_END
IFVERB LISTEN -1
   ECHO PLAYER The soft sound of waves lapping against stone echoes around the cave.
ENDIF
