NUMBER 1225
NAME Underground Lake
CAVE
DARKNESS
REGION 15
CHANNEL 68
MONSTER_GROUP 50
CALL 69
MINEA
CALL 33
*DESCRIPTION_START
The tunnel abruptly opens out into a huge cathedral-like space. Ages
past, part of the floor caved in, worn through by a fast-flowing stream.
A wide subterranean lake now fills most of the cavern, icy cold and
smelling faintly of minerals. Some hardy fish, blind, swim slowly about
in the clear water. Light shines a long way down and creates rippling
reflections on the lake bottom far below. A column of bubbles rises from
beneath a rocky overhang on the far side of the lake, deep beneath the
surface. Time and the waves have left a wide shore of coarse dark sand.
*DESCRIPTION_END
