; tiny spiral azure shell (in the sand)
; Yes, they can take it, but they can only get one per day since it's only restored at reboot.
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAMINE 0
The ceiling is lower than is comfortable for the average human, but
considering that nature alone crafted this, it is quite large and sturdy.
*DESCRIPTION_END
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAMINE 1
The gently lapping waves are soothing to the eye and ear. Tall, delicate
