NUMBER 1226
NAME Twisted Spire
CAVE
DARKNESS
REGION 15
CHANNEL 68
MONSTER_GROUP 50
CALL 69
MINEA
CALL 33
*DESCRIPTION_START
A massive column of dark stone rises up from the floor in the center of
this cavern. There is a spiral pattern to it that almost resembles a
huge unicorn's horn. It glistens in the spray from the turbulent stream
that rushes out from an opening at its base, seemingly blocking passage
any further. The water flows down a passageway that once led even deeper
underground, through the chinks between the tumbled rocks and boulders
that now block the tunnel.
*DESCRIPTION_END
EXIT NW 1223
EXIT NE 1224
ITEM 0 426 ADJ1=705 ADJ2=347 ADJ3=345
; swirling white water stream (to Nightwater Rapids)
EXTEND 0 full of tumbled boulders and rocks
ITEM 1 1627 ADJ1=189 ADJ2=329 ADJ3=306
; massive towering spiral column (since the spire item is not hidden and would look silly)
EXTEND 1 of flawless black marble
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAMINE 0
Almost a small river, this broad stream surges from the base of the
spire like a wild animal suddenly released from captivity. The water
is much warmer than it has been in other areas of the caves.
*DESCRIPTION_END
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAMINE 1
Thin veins of white and charcoal gray trace through the jet-black marble.
They pulse faintly with a ghostly light out of the corner of the eye, in
a slow but unchanging rhythm. Water trickles down the spirals in a swift
glitter to join the stream below. The spire tapers from its wide base to
a narrow tip that nearly touches the ceiling.
*DESCRIPTION_END
IFPREVERB LISTEN -1
   CLEARVERB
   ECHO PLAYER Over the thunder of the water, you hear a slow sound like a giant heartbeat.
   ECHO OTHERS %N listens carefully with a faintly disturbed expression on %h face.
ENDIF
IFVERB RECALL 0
   IFVAR SKILL32 > 3
      ECHO PLAYER Volcanic activity far beneath the surface might account for the warm
      ECHO PLAYER temperature of the water, but it is unusual considering that all the
      ECHO PLAYER other water down here has been icy cold. Perhaps the stream has its
      ECHO PLAYER origin much farther below the ground than it seems.
   ENDIF
ENDIF
IFPREVERB GO 0
   CLEARVERB
   DISBAND
   ECHO PLAYER You clamber down amongst the boulders and let the current carry you downstream.
   ECHO OTHERS %N clambers down amongst the boulders and lets the current carry %i downstream.
   RANDOM CAVEIN 1 50 0
      IFVAR CAVEIN < 4
         DAMAGEPLR CRUSH 25 You are smashed painfully up against a rock on your way through.
      ENDIF
   MOVE 1227
   AFFECT 1227
   ECHO OTHERS %N tumbles in, washed up through a crevice between two boulders.
   AFFECT 1226
ENDIF
IFVERB RECALL 1
   IFVAR SKILL32 > 3
      ECHO PLAYER The rhythm of the ethereal glimmer matches that of the strange, deep
      ECHO PLAYER beat that thrums throughout the cavern. There is no apparent source
      ECHO PLAYER for either the light or the sound.
   ENDIF
ENDIF
IFTOUCH 1
   ECHO PLAYER The rock is warm to the touch, nearly the temperature of a living thing.
ENDIF
IFPREVERB BREAK 1
   IFVAR MONSTERTIME ! TIM
      CLEARVERB
      ECHO PLAYER A deafening peal of sound rings out from the spire as you attempt to damage it!
      ECHO OTHERS A deafening peal of sound rings out from the spire as %N tries to damage it!
      DAMAGEALL BODYONLY 50 You reel in pain as the reverberations rattle your very bones.
      PLREVENT 1
      CONTPLREVENT
      ECHO ALL Those who dwell here charge into the room in response to the echoing noise.
      GENMON 63
      GENMON 63
      GENMON 62
      GENMON 62
      ; black unicorn
      ; darkweaver
      EQUAL MONSTERTIME TIM
   ENDIF
ENDIF
